    "description": "\n    <div class=\"mountain-description prose prose-stone max-w-none\">\n        <p class=\"text-lg text-stone-700 leading-relaxed mb-6\">Rising to 968 feet, Mount Philo offers one of Vermont's finest hiking experiences. \n        Whether you're seeking panoramic views, a family-friendly outing, or a quick escape into nature, \n        this peak delivers.</p>\n\n        <h2 class=\"text-xl font-bold text-stone-900 mt-8 mb-4\">Popular Routes</h2>\n        <p class=\"text-stone-600 leading-relaxed mb-4\">The most popular route, **Mount Philo Trail**, covers 1.8 miles and is rated \n    Easy. Short hike with panoramic Lake Champlain views.</p>\n\n        <h2 class=\"text-xl font-bold text-stone-900 mt-8 mb-4\">Peak Bagging</h2>\n        <div class=\"bg-emerald-50 border border-emerald-100 p-4 rounded-xl\">\n            <p class=\"text-emerald-800\">This peak offers a standalone hiking experience with minimal nearby alternatives.</p>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n    ",
